      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $47,000, a price that honestly reflects its mint condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car is in exceptional, like-new condition throughout. The exterior paint is flawless, showing no scratches, dents, chips, or swirl marks \u2014 it looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally impressive: all upholstery is pristine, all controls and electronics function perfectly, and there are no signs of wear on any surfaces. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and cooling \u2014 are in excellent working order. Service records are up to date, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. Tires have substantial tread remaining and are evenly worn. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that truly rivals a new one in every meaningful way. If you are looking for a car you can drive with complete confidence from day one, this is it.",
