      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Fair Deal for the Practical Driver!** Looking for a reliable ride without breaking the bank? This vehicle offers everyday dependability at a price that makes sense! It's in fair condition \u2014 meaning it runs well and gets the job done, though it does show some signs of wear and age inside and out. Minor cosmetic blemishes and typical use marks are present, but nothing that gets in the way of a comfortable, functional drive. If you're after a practical, no-frills vehicle that won't let you down on the daily commute, this one deserves a serious look. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll appreciate the honest value here! \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 19500.0,
